[title]
Monthly Art Contest #12: Emotion
[head]

[page]
<p>Generally-speaking, every piece of art should be emotive in one way or another. However, the point of this theme was to limit the artists to only one emotion, which yielded intense results! The emotions chosen ranged from the bread-and-butter of 'Happiness' and 'Sadness' to ones as weird as 'Upper-class-don't-give-a-flip', but all entries were intriguing to analyze.</p>

